channel.description:
Hey, i have recently been experimenting with cinema 4d and realised that since it is a modelling software i should be able to make rsps customs on it like the other softwares out there. i.e metasequioa.
I was wondering, what file extension would i have to save the model as so that i can transfer it to RsDatmaker.
thankyou very much.
